name: SVGFEGaussianBlurElement
description: The SVGFEGaussianBlurElement interface corresponds to the <feGaussianBlur> element.

members.name: SVGFEGaussianBlurElement.in1
members.description: An SVGAnimatedString corresponding to the in attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEGaussianBlurElement.stdDeviationX
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the (possibly automatically computed) X component of the stdDeviation attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEGaussianBlurElement.stdDeviationY
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the (possibly automatically computed) Y component of the stdDeviation attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEGaussianBlurElement.edgeMode
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the edgeMode attribute of the given element. Takes one of the SVG_EDGEMODE_* constants defined on this interface.

members.name: SVGFEGaussianBlurElement.setStdDeviation()
members.description: Sets the values for the stdDeviation attribute.
